CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20260408T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the May Capital Region Mesh meetup featuring a LoRa Working Group update\, a presentation on horizontal decision-making\, and a consensus session on CRM's proposed organizational charter.\n\nLocation: The Parlor at the Unitarian Universalist Church\, 274 Pleasant Street\, Concord. Google Maps: https://maps.app.goo.gl/1dg2gf1RueUyXagJ7 (Enter through the East entrance; the Parlor is on the right past the kitchenette.)\n\nTime: 7:00–9:30 PM (Space is limited — please RSVP to events@capitalmesh.net)\n\nAgenda: • 7:00–7:10 — Arrivals & Introductions • 7:10–7:45 — LoRa Working Group Update • 7:45–7:55 — Break • 7:55–8:30 — Mutual Aid Part 2: Getting Things Done • 8:30–8:40 — Break • 8:40–9:15 — Working Session: Proposed Charter • 9:15–9:30 — Closing Circle\n\nWhether you're returning or joining for the first time\, you’re welcome to attend any portion of the evening.
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260506T213000
